# ===== 白名单模式：默认忽略所有，只同步指定内容 =====

# 忽略所有
*

# === 取消忽略：需要同步的内容 ===
!.gitignore
!skills/
!skills/**
!profiles/
!profiles/**
!SOUL.md
!sync-push.sh
!sync-pull.sh

# === 排除同步目录内的运行时/缓存文件 ===
skills/.curator_backups/
skills/.usage.json
skills/.curator_state
skills/.bundled_manifest
skills/.hub/
skills/apple/

# profiles 内的缓存
profiles/*/.curator_backups/
profiles/*/.usage.json
profiles/*/.curator_state

# profiles 递归嵌套防护
profiles/profiles/

# 敏感文件
.env
*.token
*.key
auth.json
